{
  "stem": "5470.5",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't want to control these-- [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Anawayis, ?] these [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh yes, several.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Several had been back to-- and came to me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The first one, uh, coming into the camp-- that they came to me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Um, and we had several.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "One of them was Professor [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Kirido. ?] As soon as he came back from [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Theresienstadt, ?] he came to my place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, that was [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Kirido. ?] That was one of the-- the one from whom I got a message from England to get him out of the camp.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, uh, I can't say offhand how many.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But uh, altogether, I think about 30, 35 in that area.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there were many more, many more.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I don't-- or I didn't count them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was just a matter of you get your message for keeping that one out or trying to get that one out.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I-- for instance here, there's also a thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Getting people out of the camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This was a typical fellow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He worked at my office, and he was a lawyer.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But he was a bit, uh-- yeah, uneasy for himself, too.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he didn't know actually how to act.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So you had to tell him practically everything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "What to do, how to, what to.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we had, then, the green grocer was coming into the camp with a truck.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Who brought every week the, uh-- the vegetables in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they had a lot of crates.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, the only way to get him out, because leave him on his own, and he absolutely went wrong.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So his brother was there, too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was a far more acting person than he was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, uh, he said to him, OK, dress yourself.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
